    },
    {
      "title": "Include Network Infrastructure Configurations in Backup Plan",
      "description": "Ensure configurations of network infrastructure devices (e.g., routers, switches, firewalls) are part of the organization’s backup and recovery plan as well as its configuration management plan.",
      "category": "configuration",
      "page": 129
    },
    {
      "title": "Implement Dual Administrator Backup Process",
      "description": "Implement a backup and recovery process that involves at least two people: a backup administrator and a restore administrator. Both individuals should be trained to perform either role but not authorized to perform both roles simultaneously outside of critical or emergency circumstances.",
      "category": "security",
      "page": 129
    },
    {
      "title": "Regularly Test Backup and Recovery Processes",
      "description": "Ensure that the organization can reconstitute all critical data as defined in its business continuity plan and/or disaster recovery plan. Regularly test both backup and recovery processes.",
