      "page": 129
    },
    {
      "title": "Mitigate Unauthorized Data Exfiltration",
      "description": "Organizations must understand and identify all possible exit points for data, including Bluetooth, removable media, loss of devices, and other potential vulnerabilities. Protective measures should be implemented to account for all devices and connections that could serve as exit points for sensitive information.",
